{"id":375685,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":31}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"科学知识(第15期)","column":"","genre":"","count":"116","ytitle":"","mtitle":"农谚","ftitle":"","authors":["增桦","冶中","洪发"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕田不离田头，钓鱼不离滩头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多看田头，少上街头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻上场、麦上仓、黄豆扛到肩膀上，才算收了粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早起夜黄昏，一春抵两春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头薅得勤，棉花赛白银。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子收在犁上，棉花收在锄上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起早不忙，种早不慌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(增桦、冶中、洪发　搜集)"}]}